 zey hobn gezukht a gresere shtot kedey, mit a gresern yishev, mit mer yidn, kedey tsu kenen lebn dortn.

00:03:27.093 --> 00:03:30.080
tsi gedenkstu vu du host gelebt?

00:03:30.135 --> 00:03:31.916
in Byalistok? ye.

00:03:30.742 --> 00:03:31.867
in Byalistok.

00:03:31.916 --> 00:03:34.330
ikh hob gevoynt oyf ZAMENHOFA fertsn.

00:03:35.241 --> 00:03:37.126
dos iz a hoyz, tsi a dire?

00:03:36.260 --> 00:03:39.299
dos iz geven a hoyz. dos iz geven a hoyz,

00:03:39.299 --> 00:03:43.335
ober mit shkheynim nokh, mit nokh shkheynim, s'iz geven a greser hoyz.

00:03:43.335 --> 00:03:47.888
un shpeter, hobn, a dire, dos hobn mir gedungen bay yenem a dire,

00:03:47.888 --> 00:03:51.060
un shpeter hobn mir gevoynt oyf ABRIDZHNE tsen.

00:03:51.060 --> 00:03:52.980
biz mir zaynen arayn in geto.

00:03:53.880 --> 00:03:56.271
du host shvester tsi brider?

00:03:55.177 --> 00:03:59.590
ikh hob gehat a bruder, vos hot geheysn Leybl.

00:04:00.411 --> 00:04:01.781
er iz geven yunger?

00:04:01.581 --> 00:04:04.596
