00:04:02.581 --> 00:04:03.300
elter.

00:04:04.596 --> 00:04:07.973
gloyb ikh in dray un fertsiktn yor, vayl ikh bin nisht geven derbay,

00:04:08.092 --> 00:04:10.547
un ikh hob gehat a shvester,

00:04:10.921 --> 00:04:15.377
vos iz geven mit fir yor yinger far mir, Mushke Landau.

00:04:15.219 --> 00:04:15.994
Mushke.

00:04:15.773 --> 00:04:16.532
ye.

00:04:16.532 --> 00:04:18.298
un zi iz umgekumen

00:04:18.298 --> 00:04:21.973
gloyb ikh in der zelber tsayt, vayl ikh bin nisht keyn eydes, ikh bin nisht geven dan,

00:04:21.973 --> 00:04:24.355
ven m'hot likvidirt dem geto bay undz.

00:04:24.432 --> 00:04:26.483
di eltern hobn adurkhgelebt?

00:04:26.347 --> 00:04:31.851
zaynen geven in geto biz der likvidatsye, vos iz forgekumen dem zekhtsetn AUGUST,

00:04:31.851 --> 00:04:34.589
in nayntsn dray un fertsik.

00:04:34.496 --> 00:04:35.738
un nokh dem?

00:04:36.623 --> 00:04:37.574
ikh hob ze-

00:04:37.091 --> 00:04:37.645
zey...

00:04:37.574 --> 00:04:41.659
ikh hob zey farlorn, mayn mishpokhe. ikh bin avek mit a tog frier

00:04:41.659 --> 00:04:43.547
fun Byalistok,

00:04:44.942 --> 00:04:48.106
zukhn a plats tsu bahaltn mayn bruder.

00:04:48.963 --> 00:04:50.504
s'iz geven,

00:04:50.504 --> 00:04:55.184
er iz geven der eyntsiker, un mir hobn im ale gelib- gel- zeyer lib gehat.

00:04:55.261 --> 00:04:58.589
un keyn raykhe yidn zaynen mir nisht geven.

00:04:58.589 --> 00:05:02.150
ober mayne eltern zaynen geven a bisl naiv.

00:05:02.150 --> 00:05:04.640
zey hobn gegloyb-, zey hobn gegloybt in yener tsayt,

00:05:04.640 --> 00:05:07.701
di daytshn kenen nit oyfton keyn groyzame zakhn,

00:05:07.701 --> 00:05:09.340
nit tsu keyn froyen,

00:05:09.340 --> 00:05:11.849
un nisht tsu keyn eltere mener.

00:05:11.849 --> 00:05:15.050
nor dos eyntsike, zey kenen tsunemen in militer arayn

00:05:15.050 --> 00:05:18.147
a yungn bokherl, un er iz dan alt geven tsvantsik yor.

00:05:18.730 --> 00:05:24.467
iz, hot men mir gegebn a keyt, a goldene, fun mayn mamen,

00:05:24.467 --> 00:05:27.396
un epes nokh a por tsvey shtiklekh gold,

00:05:27.537 --> 00:05:31.949
ikh zol forn in a plats vu s'zaynen shoyn keyn yidn nito, s'iz likvidirt gevorn.

00:05:32.090 --> 00:05:34.269
ikh zol gebn dos a krist,

00:05:35.154 --> 00:05:39.034
un er zol oysbahaltn mayn bruder.

00:05:40.366 --> 00:05:43.226
un dan hot zikh ongehoybn mayn pekl tsores.

00:05:43.621 --> 00:05:45.289
kumendik in AUGUST,

00:05:45.834 --> 00:05:48.913
in, dos iz geven in nayntsn dray un fertsik,

00:05:48.913 --> 00:05:50.715
dem fuftsetn AUGUST,

00:05:51.430 --> 00:05:56.320
hot men mir oyfn gas, a kleyn yingele, mistame fun nayn, tsen yor,

00:05:56.320 --> 00:05:58.830
tsugegangen tsu mir un hot ongevizn mitn finger un gezogt,

00:05:58.830 --> 00:06:00.438
"dos iz a yidishe."

00:06:00.705 --> 00:06:04.608
un in meshekh fun finf minut, vi ikh hob probirt opleykenen,

00:06:04.642 --> 00:06:09.274
vayl ikh hob getrogn dan a vayse kleydl, a zumerdike, punkt vi ale

00:06:09.274 --> 00:06:11.657
goyim geyen, ikh hob aropgenumen di lates,

00:06:11.657 --> 00:06:15.103
ober dokh hot mir nisht gegolfn. un ikh bin glaykh,

00:06:15.103 --> 00:06:17.905
tsugekumen a daytsh, m'hot mir glaykh fararestirt.

00:06:20.067 --> 00:06:23.437
dortn bin ikh geven a vokh tsayt,

00:06:24.641 --> 00:06:27.415
ober ikh volt zikh gevolt umkern tsurik,

00:06:27.662 --> 00:06:30.490
far der milkhome, tsu redn vegn mayn mishpokhe,

00:06:30.490 --> 00:06:31.904
vegn mayne eltern.

00:06:32.045 --> 00:06:34.436
 vos far a shtub ikh hob gegat.

00:06:35.258 --> 00:06:38.124
mit vemen ikh bin ertsoygn gevorn.

00:06:47.591 --> 00:06:50.733
in a shtub fun a sakh varemkeyt, un a sakh libe.

00:06:51.299 --> 00:06:55.357
nisht keyn raykhe mentshn, ober forgeshritene.

00:06:55.357 --> 00:06:58.350
mayn tate iz geven aktiv in a so- a sotsyalist,

00:07:08.703 --> 00:07:12.925
er iz geven zeyer a aktiver mentsh, a mentsh vos hot geleyent di prese tog-teglekh.

00:07:13.746 --> 00:07:20.201
un vi ikh hob frier gezogt, naiv. er hot nisht gegloybt az s'ken zikh iberkhazern, az az daytshn kenen ton azelkhe zakhn.

00:07:20.575 --> 00:07:22.569
ober er hot undz gegebn

00:07:22.569 --> 00:07:24.627
a oysergeveynlekhe ertsiung,

00:07:24.627 --> 00:07:26.463
a mentshlekhe, a vareme,

00:07:26.463 --> 00:07:28.612
a yidishe in der ershter rey,

00:07:28.612 --> 00:07:31.563
traditsyonele yidn zaynen mir geven,

00:07:32.044 --> 00:07:37.733
un mir hobn ale farkukt tsu dem bruder mitn tatn.

00:07:38.909 --> 00:07:40.988
ken ikh nemen a UNK mir?

00:07:46.866 --> 00:07:49.271
un mayn mame vi a yidishe mame,

00:07:49.271 --> 00:07:51.271
hot geton alts in der velt

00:07:51.271 --> 00:07:53.775
makhn undzer heym beser un shener.

00:07:54.086 --> 00:07:56.660
s'iz geven a freylekh heym, un a varem heym,

00:07:56.660 --> 00:08:01.094
ale yunge mentshn zaynen gekumen tsu undz, in mayn kleyner hoyz,

00:08:01.425 --> 00:08:06.140
zaynen tog-ayn un tog-oys gekumen tsendliker yunge mentshn, m'hot gezesn baym tish,

00:08:06.140 --> 00:08:09.972
un efsher nisht geven, nisht geven keyn CAKES un s'iz nisht geven keyn gute zakhn,

00:08:09.972 --> 00:08:14.008
ober mir hobn gehat a gute yugnt, a vareme.

00:08:14.063 --> 00:08:18.072
un vi kinder zaynen mir oykh arayn in der yugnt-organizatsye.

00:08:19.021 --> 00:08:23.370
un mir zaynen azoy ertsoygn gevorn, mit azoy fil varemkeyt, mit libshaft,

00:08:23.370 --> 00:08:24.291
beemes,

00:08:24.291 --> 00:08:27.163
vi lang ikh vel lebn vel ikh es gedenken.

00:08:28.276 --> 00:08:29.922
un ye-

00:08:28.574 --> 00:08:30.262
vi hot geheysn di organizatsye?

00:08:30.003 --> 00:08:35.227
dos hot geheysn der Skif, bay der yugnt fun Tsukunft. dos iz geven di organizatsye.

00:08:35.227 --> 00:08:37.178
un aleyn bin ikh gegangen

00:08:37.616 --> 00:08:40.780
biz dem oysbrukh fun der milkhome in a yidishe folkshul.

00:08:40.780 --> 00:08:42.960
un dos iz mayn gantse bildung, vayle

00:08:42.960 --> 00:08:45.163
s'iz nisht geven keyn meglekhkeyt, un ikh bin glaykh

00:08:45.163 --> 00:08:47.360
arayn in geto, un dos iz es geven.

00:08:47.360 --> 00:08:50.220
ober ikh hob gegendikt a Mikhalevitsh-shul, a folkshul.

00:08:51.850 --> 00:08:55.816
dos iz mayn bagazh fun bildung zayendik in yene ts- in yene tsaytn.

00:08:57.318 --> 00:09:00.390
un dan vil ikh, ikh vil zikh umkern tsurik tsu

00:09:00.390 --> 00:09:01.716
⟨Byalistok⟩.

