ye.

00:09:02.870 --> 00:09:04.050
oyb ikh meg fregn,

00:09:03.824 --> 00:09:04.561
bite.

00:09:04.430 --> 00:09:06.800
velkhe shprakh hot ir geredt in der heym?

00:09:06.701 --> 00:09:08.780
in der heym hobn mir geredt oysshlislekh yidish.

00:09:08.780 --> 00:09:14.418
mir hobn nisht genitst keyn ander shprakh. vayl mir hobn zikh nisht gemisht mit di polyakn tsu fil, hobn mir nisht be-

00:09:14.418 --> 00:09:16.736
ober mir hobn gekent ale redn poylish,

00:09:16.736 --> 00:09:21.481
s'iz natirlekh geven, dos iz geven di shprakh fun land. un mayne eltern hobn geredt rusish.

00:09:22.160 --> 00:09:24.077
dos iz vayle, far der,

00:09:24.077 --> 00:09:28.183
nokh der ershter velt-milkhome, ikh veys, hobn zey geredt rusish un ertsoygn gevorn mit rusish.

00:09:28.183 --> 00:09:30.517
zey hobn beyde geredt rusish tsvishn zikh.

00:09:30.871 --> 00:09:33.375
un der Mikhalovitsh-shul iz geven bloyz far yidn.

00:09:32.679 --> 00:09:35.964
a a yidishe folkshul. oysshlislekh a yidishe folkshul.

00:09:35.700 --> 00:09:38.156
hostu gehat goyishe fraynd?

00:09:38.317 --> 00:09:41.119
keyn mol nisht. keyn mol nisht.

00:09:39.296 --> 00:09:40.236
keyn mol nit?

00:09:41.119 --> 00:09:42.885
mir hobn zikh nisht gemisht mit di,

00:09:42.885 --> 00:09:44.538
mit di polyakn bay undz.

00:09:44.572 --> 00:09:47.006
un di eltern oykh hobn nisht gehat?

00:09:46.275 --> 00:09:48.411
NO, keyn poylishe fraynd, NO.

00:09:48.402 --> 00:09:50.150
AND dortn vu ir hot gevoynt

00:09:50.150 --> 00:09:52.219
hot ir gehat goyishe shkheynim?

00:09:53.120 --> 00:09:54.694
ikh gloyb koym.

00:09:54.694 --> 00:09:56.736
mir hobn nisht gegat. zeyer vintsik.

00:09:56.736 --> 00:09:58.566
vayle di gegnt iz geven,

00:09:58.566 --> 00:10:05.687
ikh veys, efsher hobn mir vi yidn zikh aleyn gemakht a geto in di normale tsaytn. mir hobn gevoynt ts- kontsentrirt yidn tsuzamen

00:10:05.784 --> 00:10:06.942
mit zikh.

00:10:07.359 --> 00:10:12.720
ikh hob gevolt fregn az a mol ven ir zent geven oyf der veg fun shul oder tsu shul,

00:10:12.720 --> 00:10:16.480
hot ir gehat instantsn ven me hot tsugetshepet

00:10:14.125 --> 00:10:15.644
ye, be-

00:10:16.480 --> 00:10:18.240
derfar vos ir zayt geven yidn?

