NO, ikh gede- NO NO NO, ikh gedenk nisht di ale zakhn, NO. az s'iz durkhgegangen a meydl, hot men zikh, m'hot geredt tsu zi- tsvishn zikh,

00:10:24.400 --> 00:10:26.878
ober mir zaynen nisht geven keyn fraynd.

00:10:30.103 --> 00:10:32.054
un vos gedenkt ir fun,

00:10:32.054 --> 00:10:33.693
bay di yontoyvim,

00:10:33.693 --> 00:10:38.537
di mishpokhe, di mame hot gehat a groyse mishpokhe, me flegt tsunoyfkumen un...

00:10:38.295 --> 00:10:38.905
d-

00:10:38.905 --> 00:10:41.778
di noentkeyt nisht nor vos iz mayn,

00:10:41.778 --> 00:10:45.693
mayn familye, di kleyne familye vos mir zaynen geven ts- a bruder un shvester,

00:10:45.693 --> 00:10:52.309
BUT mayn mame's mishpokhe iz geven oykh ⟨heyst⟩, azoy k- gebundn, geknipt un gebundn, zaynen geven tsuzamen,

00:10:52.309 --> 00:10:56.777
yedn yontev zaynen mir geven tsuzamen. ale shvester zaynen gekumen mit zeyere kinder.

00:10:56.777 --> 00:11:00.777
un s'iz geven, s'iz geven beemes a yontev bay undz. s'iz geven yontev.

00:11:00.777 --> 00:11:04.351
ober khuts dem, dakht zikh mir, oybe s'iz geven zibn teg a vokh,

00:11:04.351 --> 00:11:07.372
iz zibn teg a vokh hobn mir gezen di mishpokhe, mayn mame's.

00:11:07.372 --> 00:11:09.132
zaynen ale gekumen tsu geyn.

00:11:09.592 --> 00:11:15.245
m'iz gegangen koyfn tsuzamen. m'iz gegangen kokhn tsuzamen. m'hot altsding geton tsuzamen. s'iz geven a noentkeyt oysergeveynlekh,

00:11:15.245 --> 00:11:19.515
un m'hot nisht gevoynt vayt eyner fun andern, m'hot gevoynt zeyer noent eyner fun andern.

00:11:20.549 --> 00:11:23.579
vi hot geheysn di bobes un zey- mit di zeydes?

00:11:23.315 --> 00:11:30.181
ikh ken nor zogn vegn eyne vos hot gevoynt mit undz. zi hot farlorn yung dem man, zi iz geven etl- zeks un fuftsik, zibn un fuftsik,

00:11:30.181 --> 00:11:32.713
iz mayn mame iz geven di eltste shvester,

00:11:32.713 --> 00:11:35.962
hot zi ir gebrakht tsu undz, un di bobe hot gevoynt mit undz ale yorn.

00:11:35.570 --> 00:11:36.810
vi hot zi geheysn?

00:11:36.400 --> 00:11:38.456
Yente n- Turek.

00:11:38.251 --> 00:11:39.746
Yente Turek.

00:11:38.456 --> 00:11:40.195
Turek, ye.

00:11:39.952 --> 00:11:43.391
OKAY, dos iz geven ava- avade di mame's mame, ye.

00:11:42.101 --> 00:11:44.854
der mame's mame, ye, der mame's mame.

00:11:43.391 --> 00:11:45.405
ye, ye, gut.

00:11:45.697 --> 00:11:48.131
un vos gedenkstu fun Byalistok?

00:11:49.271 --> 00:11:52.052
Byalistok iz geven a yidishe shtot.

00:11:52.052 --> 00:11:54.280
loyt mayn opshatsung,

00:11:54.633 --> 00:11:57.280
zi hot gehat zekhtsik toyznt yidn,

00:11:58.442 --> 00:11:59.925
zeyer aktive.

00:11:59.925 --> 00:12:01.563
a prekhtike yugnt,

00:12:01.563 --> 00:12:03.349
ober a yidishe yugnt.

00:12:03.349 --> 00:12:07.775
vayle bay undz, oybe s'iz geven in di klenere shtetlekh, iz men gegangen,

00:12:07.775 --> 00:12:10.258
m'hot geredt poylish, m'hot zikh bamit

00:12:10.653 --> 00:12:15.740
avektsugeyn funem yidish. iz Byalistok, ven du host gegangen oyf di hoypt-gasn, hostu gehert fun yunge

00:12:15.740 --> 00:12:17.690
inteligente mentshn redn yidish.

00:12:18.611 --> 00:12:20.981
farshteyst? s'iz geven a yidishe gimnazye,

00:12:21.079 --> 00:12:23.428
ef- zeks yidishe folkshuln,

00:12:24.717 --> 00:12:30.576
un a kh- a skhum fun zekhtsik toyznt yidn, dos iz a sakh. un zekhtsik toyznt yidn hobn zikh oysgelebt.

00:12:30.780 --> 00:12:33.230
tsienistishe organizatsyes,

00:12:33.230 --> 00:12:35.434
sotsyalistishe organizatsyes,

00:12:35.434 --> 00:12:37.853
s'iz geven a zeyer zeyer

00:12:37.865 --> 00:12:40.483
aktive shtot, a aktive shtot.

00:12:40.142 --> 00:12:42.321
in vos hobn di yidn zikh basheftikt?

00:12:43.206 --> 00:12:45.597
fun shusteray, shnayderay,

00:12:45.695 --> 00:12:50.874
kabtsonim, a groyse protsent, a ka- zeyer a groyse protsent oreme-layt,

00:12:51.418 --> 00:12:56.837
ober mir hobn gegat institutsyes groyse, vi lines-khoylim un nokh andere,

00:12:56.837 --> 00:12:58.305
velkhe hobn geholfn,

00:12:58.305 --> 00:13:01.193
geholfn eyne dem andern. ober yidn zaynen,

00:13:01.248 --> 00:13:03.944
s'iz geven a protsent, a kle- efsher

00:13:03.944 --> 00:13:07.460
tsen protse- zeyer raykhe yidn, zeyer, vos zaynen geven fabrikant.

00:13:07.460 --> 00:13:11.480
di gantse shtot iz geven a tekstil-shtot, farshteyst? azoyernokh,

00:13:11.480 --> 00:13:13.369
zaynen geven yidishe fabrikantn,

00:13:13.369 --> 00:13:19.150
zeyer zeltn iz geven a kri- a goy vos iz geven a, a fabrikant.

00:13:19.354 --> 00:13:24.110
un s'iz geven a protsent fun yidishe, un sokhrim, der grester teyl sokhrim un tekstil.

00:13:24.110 --> 00:13:26.120
tekstil-arbeter, zeyer a sakh.

00:13:26.418 --> 00:13:29.767
ts- vos mit tsaytungen, teaters?

00:13:28.077 --> 00:13:33.511
ye, YES, mir hobn gegat a yidishn shtendikn teater, vos hot gegeysn TEATER-PALAS,

00:13:33.737 --> 00:13:36.943
mir hobn glaykhtsaytik gehat

00:13:36.943 --> 00:13:40.454
dray tsu fir tog-teglekhe tsaytung, onheybn fun

00:13:40.454 --> 00:13:42.326
Haynt, di,

00:13:42.326 --> 00:13:44.454
ikh gedenk nisht di nemen.

00:13:44.454 --> 00:13:46.113
Haynt, der F-

00:13:46.113 --> 00:13:49.383
Folks-Tsaytung iz aro- gekumen tsu undz,

00:13:49.383 --> 00:13:55.298
kh'zog, mir, f- zeks, efsher zeks tsu zibn tsaytungen. yeder organizatsye hot gegat ⟨dray tog-⟩, a teglekhe tsaytung.

00:13:56.247 --> 00:13:59.234
un vifl shuln zaynen geven in Byalistok?

00:14:00.289 --> 00:14:05.148
shuln iz geven zeyer a sakh. s'iz geven di hoypt-shul vos hot geheysn ⟨bay undz der⟩,

00:14:05.246 --> 00:14:09.740
di g- di, ven der daytsh iz arayn hot er arayngevorfn dortn etlekhe toyznt yidn,

00:14:09.740 --> 00:14:15.112
mener. un er hot farbrent mit der shul. dos iz geven dos ershte tog ven, ve- der ershter, tsveyter tog ven er iz arayn

00:14:15.112 --> 00:14:16.453
keyn Byalistok.

00:14:16.453 --> 00:14:18.687
ober s'iz geven shuln un bes-midroshim,

00:14:18.687 --> 00:14:22.368
oyf yedn vinkele fun shtot avu di yidn hobn nor gevoynt zaynen geven

00:14:22.368 --> 00:14:24.000
shuln.

00:14:25.905 --> 00:14:28.900
gedenkstu az du bist a mol aroysgeforn fun Byalistok in

00:14:28.900 --> 00:14:31.120
tsu di arumike shtetlekh oder shtet?

00:14:31.160 --> 00:14:39.367
ye, ikh bin geven in Grodne, ikh bin geven in Lomzhe, ikh bin geven in a sakh shtetlekh. vayl, vos iz geven, di yidn vos zaynen geven in yidishe organizatsyes flegn mir forn,

00:14:39.367 --> 00:14:42.686
me flegt nemen a rover un aroysforn in a shtetl arum zikh.

00:14:42.686 --> 00:14:46.494
demolt, s'iz geven aza min shtetl ⟨vi⟩ Zabludeve, oykh a yidishe shtetele.

00:14:46.494 --> 00:14:48.680
un di yugnt,

00:14:49.075 --> 00:14:53.686
i- ikh veys nit, efsher vayl ikh hob zikh gedreyt in di krayzn fun di yugntlekhe,

00:14:53.686 --> 00:14:55.388
zaynen alts geven,

00:14:55.388 --> 00:14:58.381
zey hobn gehert tsu organizatsyes, un s'iz geven

00:14:58.883 --> 00:15:00.956
nisht politish rayf, nor

00:15:00.956 --> 00:15:03.686
zaynen geven bavustzinike yunge mentshn.

00:15:03.686 --> 00:15:04.409
farshteyst?

00:15:04.409 --> 00:15:08.970
azoyernokh, vu du host gekumen hostu gefunen a organizatsye tsu vemen tsu kumen un tsu vemen tsu redn.

00:15:11.050 --> 00:15:12.317
⟨dos zaynen...⟩

00:15:12.733 --> 00:15:15.950
iz dayn shteyger lebn iz geven a guter?

00:15:15.550 --> 00:15:19.784
a, zeyer, zeyer. mayn lebn iz geven a glentsnder.

00:15:19.784 --> 00:15:27.423
nisht gekukt oyf dem, vayl s'iz geven redifes fun oyf yidn in Poyln, s'iz geven altsding, un s'iz geven bagrenetsungen gevise,

00:15:27.423 --> 00:15:30.599
ober vi a kind, zayendik mit mayn mishpokhe,

00:15:30.599 --> 00:15:32.089
iz mir geven zeyer gut.

00:15:32.089 --> 00:15:37.848
vayl ikh muz nokh untershtraykhn, dos iz alts a dank mayn tatn mit mayn mamen, vayle zey hobn geshafn

00:15:37.924 --> 00:15:42.450
di vareme atmosfere bay undz in der heym, un zey hobn gesh- undz gegebn

00:15:42.450 --> 00:15:46.131
di meglekhkeyt zikh oystsuklaybn vos mir viln ton, vu mir viln zayn,

00:15:46.131 --> 00:15:48.060
un zey hobn undz gevizn dem veg.

00:15:48.060 --> 00:15:51.124
mir zaynen geven politish kh-, politish, vi kinder

00:15:51.124 --> 00:15:55.854
hobn mir gevust vos far tsiln mir hobn in lebn, tsu vos mir viln epes dergreykhn.

00:15:55.854 --> 00:15:58.337
i durkh lernen un durkh arbet.

00:15:58.882 --> 00:16:00.635
dos iz geven undzer tsil.

00:16:00.817 --> 00:16:05.109
ven gedenkstu az dos zol alts onheybn

00:16:05.109 --> 00:16:10.443
tsu vern andersh, in zibn, akht un draysikstn yor, nayn un draysikstn yor?

00:16:09.626 --> 00:16:13.598
ikh vil dir zogn, ikh hob, ikh, ven ikh red vegn zikh perzenlekh,

00:16:13.598 --> 00:16:16.337
ikh hob dos nisht gefilt in zibn un draysiktn yor.

00:16:16.711 --> 00:16:21.315
undzere tsores hobn zikh ongehoybn in nayntsn nayn un draysik.

00:16:20.649 --> 00:16:21.863
vos iz geshen?

00:16:21.541 --> 00:16:24.534
nayntsn nayn un draysik, ven s'hot zikh ongehoybn di milkhome

00:16:24.534 --> 00:16:25.507
tsvi-,

00:16:25.507 --> 00:16:28.825
dos ershte iz bay undz arayn der daytsh

00:16:29.434 --> 00:16:35.230
in nayntsn nayn un draysik, vayl ikh bin fun di farnumene gebitn vos di rusn hobn shpeter farnumen.

00:16:35.230 --> 00:16:36.534
iz dortn

00:16:36.534 --> 00:16:39.230
zaynen di daytshn geven a vokh tsayt, nisht mer.

00:16:40.051 --> 00:16:45.442
un zey hobn dan farbrent epes etlekhe toyznt mener, vi ikh hob gezogt, in shul,

00:16:47.788 --> 00:16:51.165
un in meshekh fun der vokh hot zikh ongehoybn shreklekhe redifes.

00:16:51.242 --> 00:16:52.831
in a vokh shpeter,

00:16:52.831 --> 00:16:56.059
ven zey hobn gemakht dem opmakh m-, di rusn mit di daytshn,

00:16:56.263 --> 00:16:58.335
zaynen di daytshn fun undz avek.

00:16:58.859 --> 00:17:02.044
un ikh bin geven fun nayn un draysik

00:17:02.044 --> 00:17:04.350
biz eyn un fertsik mit di rusn.

00:17:04.350 --> 00:17:06.220
di rusn hobn bay undz farnumen.

00:17:06.630 --> 00:17:10.782
un dan iz geven shvere yorn der-, shvere yorn mit dem

00:17:10.880 --> 00:17:12.661
vos oybe du host gehat a kreml

00:17:12.661 --> 00:17:16.554
bistu gevorn a kapitalist loyt di rusn, di opshatsung. hostu gehat moyre.

00:17:16.554 --> 00:17:19.150
m'hot dos glaykh tsugenumen, men hot es likvidirt,

00:17:19.150 --> 00:17:23.192
ober zayendik a yugntlekhe, bin ikh tsurikgegangen in shul a bisl.

00:17:23.192 --> 00:17:24.661
ikh hob nisht gearbet,

00:17:24.661 --> 00:17:28.186
un ikh bin geven fray, vayle m'hot mir nisht geroydeft vi a yid.

00:17:28.186 --> 00:17:29.171
farshteyst?

00:17:29.171 --> 00:17:31.207
di tsvey yor zaynen geven,

00:17:31.858 --> 00:17:35.426
un zayendik yung trakhtstu nisht,

00:17:35.426 --> 00:17:39.080
du trakhtst nisht vegn di politishe lage, tsi di- tsi za-

00:17:39.080 --> 00:17:42.150
du host gelofn, du host gegangen, du host getantst, du host,

00:17:42.150 --> 00:17:44.511
ikh bin gegangen in shule, s'iz mir geven gut.

00:17:44.511 --> 00:17:46.931
un ikh bin geven mit mayn gantse mishpokhe.

00:17:46.943 --> 00:17:49.335
vayl zeyer a sakh yidn

00:17:49.901 --> 00:17:53.080
hot men aroysgeshikt. di rusn zaynen arayn,

00:17:53.850 --> 00:17:58.090
un di vos zaynen geven a bisl mer farmeglekh hobn zey farshikt keyn Sibir.

00:17:59.411 --> 00:18:06.447
mir hobn a bisele moyre gehat, vayle i mayn tate iz geven a Bundist vos iz geven bay zey a kontrerevolutsyoner bay di rusn,

00:18:06.447 --> 00:18:11.717
i glaykhtsaytik mir hobn gehat a kleyne kreml, hobn mir moyre gehat az mir zaynen fun di yidn

00:18:11.717 --> 00:18:13.419
vos m'vet oykh aroysshikn.

00:18:13.419 --> 00:18:15.085
nor nokh dray monatn

00:18:15.085 --> 00:18:18.553
hot men undz nisht aroysgeshikt, un der lebn hot zikh ayngeshtelt.

00:18:18.553 --> 00:18:21.015
mir hobn gelebt tsvey yor mit di rusn.

00:18:26.048 --> 00:18:30.759
mir hobn gegat alemen. mir hobn gehat di gantse mishpokhe mit, ye, keyner hot nisht gefelt.

00:18:31.282 --> 00:18:36.631
un undzere tsores hobn zikh ongefangen in nayntsn eyn un fertsik.

00:18:38.176 --> 00:18:39.060
zog mir vegn dem.

00:18:38.910 --> 00:18:39.470
ye.

00:18:42.112 --> 00:18:45.312
ven s'hot zikh ongefangen di milkhome, di daytshn,

00:18:45.729 --> 00:18:47.807
z- hobn ibergef-,

00:18:48.070 --> 00:18:50.509
s'iz geven aza min kurtser peryod,

00:18:50.509 --> 00:18:52.332
in nayntsn eyn un fertsik,

00:18:53.154 --> 00:18:56.183
ikh trakht tsi ikh makh nisht keyn toes in der date.

00:18:58.388 --> 00:19:02.354
zaynen arayn in nayntsn nayn un draysik, fertsik, eyn un fertsik, gloyb ikh.

00:19:02.537 --> 00:19:04.679
ven zey zaynen arayngekumen hobn di,

00:19:04.679 --> 00:19:06.758
hobn di di daytshn

00:19:07.679 --> 00:19:13.481
arayngefirt keyn Byalistok hunderter vagonen, hot dos gegeysn

00:19:13.494 --> 00:19:15.019
mit shteyn-koyln.

00:19:15.019 --> 00:19:16.609
du veyst vos iz shteyn-koyln?

00:19:16.218 --> 00:19:16.739
neyn.

00:19:16.609 --> 00:19:18.651
dos iz mit vos men heytst.

00:19:18.855 --> 00:19:19.715
ah.

00:19:19.494 --> 00:19:20.190
ye?

00:19:20.977 --> 00:19:26.481
un ale zaynen geven ibertsaygt az dos zaynen shteyn-koyln, zey hobn geshtanen oyfn, oyfn vokzal,

00:19:26.940 --> 00:19:28.566
shteyn-koyln,

00:19:28.834 --> 00:19:31.402
un in meshekh fun dray teg,

00:19:31.402 --> 00:19:34.806
ven s'hot zikh ongehoybn mm Daytshland hot derklert di milkhome,

00:19:34.806 --> 00:19:37.714
hot men geefnt di vagonen, zey zaynen aroysgemarshirt

00:19:37.897 --> 00:19:39.572
fun di vagonen,

00:19:39.572 --> 00:19:42.863
hunderter hunderter t- daytshishe zelner.

00:19:43.536 --> 00:19:46.019
un zey zaynen glaykh arayn in shtot.

00:19:46.019 --> 00:19:47.210
azoyernokh,

00:19:47.210 --> 00:19:51.359
normal in andere erter, eyder di daytshn zaynen arayn, di rusn zaynen aroys,

00:19:51.359 --> 00:19:54.210
hobn yidn gehat a meglekhkeyt

00:19:54.210 --> 00:19:55.955
tsu loyfn, loyfn mit di rusn,

00:19:55.955 --> 00:19:58.714
vayle mit di rusn oybe du host gekent derloyfn tsu ergets

00:19:58.714 --> 00:20:01.522
hot dos gegeysn rateven zikh dem lebn.

00:20:01.981 --> 00:20:06.905
bay undz zaynen ober di daytshn arayn nokh tsvey dray teg, un du host nisht gehat keyn shum meglekhkeytn.

00:20:07.024 --> 00:20:09.777
un dan hot zikh ongehoybn undzere tsores.

00:20:10.684 --> 00:20:11.741
ikh bin ge-

00:20:11.741 --> 00:20:14.798
z- meshekh fun fir vokhn hobn zey geshafn a geto,

00:20:16.811 --> 00:20:18.294
un me...

00:20:16.833 --> 00:20:19.309
dertseyl mir vegn dem. vos meynt a geto?

00:20:18.980 --> 00:20:23.969
a geto iz men tsamt dir op fun ale zaytn,

00:20:24.066 --> 00:20:26.989
me git dir eyn shtikl, a teyl fun shtot,

00:20:27.257 --> 00:20:31.521
un dortn zaynen kontsentrirt ale yidn.

00:20:31.521 --> 00:20:35.053
lomir zogn fun zekhtsik toyznt tsu ikh veys, efsher a teyl kh- nisht UNK,

00:20:35.053 --> 00:20:36.989
zaynen arayn in dem geto,

00:20:37.130 --> 00:20:40.181
ah ikh veys, fuftsik, etlekhe fuftsik toyznt,

00:20:40.300 --> 00:20:41.521
un

00:20:43.130 --> 00:20:45.399
un men hot undz ale opgeshlosn.

00:20:45.399 --> 00:20:50.521
di yidn in geto hobn zikh geshafn zayn eygene regirung, vos hot gegeysn yudnrat.

00:20:52.087 --> 00:20:57.053
un da- di tsores in dem geto iz nisht tsu bashraybn.

00:20:57.682 --> 00:20:59.336
mir hobn keyn esn nisht gegat,

00:20:59.336 --> 00:21:00.925
mir hobn gehungert dortn,

00:21:01.044 --> 00:21:04.031
s'iz geven nisht keyn mentshlekhe badingungen.

00:21:04.406 --> 00:21:05.804
yeder, farshteyst,

00:21:05.804 --> 00:21:09.760
mentshn hobn gevoynt in der ander ek shtot, men hot zikh gedarft klaybn in geto arayn.

00:21:09.760 --> 00:21:12.286
un dos hot men dir gegebn fir un tsvantsik sho

00:21:12.320 --> 00:21:14.201
zikh tsu klaybn in geto.

00:21:14.426 --> 00:21:15.541
tomer nit?

00:21:15.341 --> 00:21:17.924
tomer nit shist men dir oyfn ort, vos iz do.

00:21:17.958 --> 00:21:19.870
iz men gelofn mit di peklekh,

00:21:19.870 --> 00:21:23.292
vos m'hot gekent. m'hot nisht genumen keyn mebl, m'hot nisht genumen keyn zakh,

00:21:23.292 --> 00:21:25.079
me hot genumen dos vikhtikste,

00:21:25.079 --> 00:21:29.116
un host gedarft zukhn a tsimer bay imetsn vos hot gevoynt in yener gegnt.

00:21:30.596 --> 00:21:37.206
un dos iz geven undzer geto. in dem geto hobn mir gevoynt tsvey yor tsayt. mir hobn gekrign dortn a di- a tsimer,

00:21:37.206 --> 00:21:39.483
bar tsvey tsvey

00:21:39.483 --> 00:21:42.738
froyen vos zey hobn gevoynt aleyn. zey hobn gegat dortn a APARTMENT

00:21:42.738 --> 00:21:44.774
fun tsvey tsimern mit a kikh.

00:21:45.000 --> 00:21:48.887
hobn zey undz opgegebn eyn tsimer. m'hot zey getsvungen az zey zoln undz opgebn a tsimer,

00:21:48.887 --> 00:21:52.908
zaynen mir arayn, finef mentshn in eyn tsimer

00:21:52.908 --> 00:21:53.866
bay yenem.

00:21:54.280 --> 00:21:56.157
dortn hobn mir gevoynt.

00:21:56.319 --> 00:21:57.354
biz m'hot,

00:21:57.354 --> 00:22:00.859
m'hot opgeshnitn dem geto, men hot im vayter farklenert,

00:22:00.978 --> 00:22:04.901
un men hot undz geshikt oyf an ander dire, oyf ABRIDZHNE tsen.

00:22:06.169 --> 00:22:09.369
vi azoy hot, vos hot men geton mitn, mit der tsayt?

00:22:09.744 --> 00:22:12.752
mit der tsayt, di daytshn hobn geshafn

00:22:10.218 --> 00:22:10.848
UNK

00:22:14.700 --> 00:22:16.270
nutslekhe yidn

00:22:17.340 --> 00:22:22.731
velkhe hobn gegarbet. vos zey hobn, s'hot genutst, vos zey hobn gekent oysnitsn.

00:22:22.956 --> 00:22:28.396
a d- aza min grupe flegt aroysgeyn yedn frimorgn oysern geto,

00:22:28.396 --> 00:22:30.773
bay di geto iz geven a toyer,

00:22:31.084 --> 00:22:33.709
un dortn zaynen geshtanen tsvey dray daytshn,

00:22:33.709 --> 00:22:35.369
fir un tsvantsik sho a tog.

00:22:35.594 --> 00:22:38.311
un zey hobn undz ⟨opgetsamt⟩ az me zol khas-vekholile nit zindikn.

00:22:38.311 --> 00:22:42.454
iz flegn zey dre- in der fri flegt men dir nemen tsu der arbet.

00:22:43.551 --> 00:22:48.517
iz, ikh bin gegangen, fun mayn mishpokhe bin ikh geven eyne aleyn vos hot gegarbet,

00:22:48.517 --> 00:22:51.620
vayl mayne eltern hobn probirt zukhn arbet in geto,

00:22:51.620 --> 00:22:54.581
vayl s'iz geven fabrikn, etlekhe fabrikn

00:22:54.658 --> 00:22:57.843
vos zey hobn ge- oysgearbet gevise zakhn,

00:22:57.843 --> 00:22:59.709
un di daytshn hobn es tsugenumen.

00:22:59.709 --> 00:23:02.821
hobn zey basheftikt di yidn fun geto,

00:23:02.821 --> 00:23:06.241
ver s'hot gekent, m'hot gedarft hobn protektsye arayntsukumen dortn.

00:23:06.700 --> 00:23:08.840
iz mayn tate geven

00:23:10.160 --> 00:23:11.890
eyner vos hot opgehit di fabrik.

00:23:13.572 --> 00:23:15.091
un mayn bruder

00:23:15.317 --> 00:23:23.198
hot mayn mame zeyer moyre gehat aroystsugeyn, vayle er iz dokh geven a yingl fun tsvantsik yor, er zol nit aroysgeyn oysern geto, vayl me hot moyre gehat farn aroysgeyn oysern geto.

00:23:23.615 --> 00:23:27.545
flegt er l- er, hot er oykh gefunen an ander fabrik,

00:23:27.545 --> 00:23:30.198
vos hot opgehitn di fabrik, s'hot dortn gearbet,

00:23:30.891 --> 00:23:35.134
un ikh bin geven di eyntsike vos iz aroys oysern geto, vayl ikh hob gekrign a broyt,

00:23:35.806 --> 00:23:38.517
kedey di mishpokhe zol kenen ongeyn mitn lebn.

00:23:38.700 --> 00:23:41.410
zayendik demolt alt zekhtsn yor s-,

00:23:41.934 --> 00:23:45.380
bin ikh geven, un ikh hob gegangen, ikh hob geton vos m'hot gegeysn. m'hot gevashn di

00:23:45.380 --> 00:23:49.565
podloges far zey, m'hot geton ale sh- ale shmutsike arbetn, vos zey hobn nor gevolt

00:23:49.565 --> 00:23:50.623
hobn mir geton.

00:23:52.210 --> 00:23:55.048
un vos iz tomer emetser iz gevorn krank?

00:23:55.656 --> 00:23:57.962
iz er geven krank, iz er gelegn in geto.

00:23:58.273 --> 00:24:02.601
un shisn iz gevorn a natirlekhe zakh, tog-ayn un tog-oys.

00:24:03.613 --> 00:24:10.220
zey zaynen arayn a kuk ton vos me tut in geto, iz shisn a mentsh iz geven oder, nor kedey undz tsu dershrekn.

00:24:10.220 --> 00:24:11.792
kedey az mir zoln moyre hobn.

00:24:12.188 --> 00:24:15.813
hobn zey, dos ershte vos zey hobn geton hobn zey oyfgehongen dray yunge mentshn

00:24:15.890 --> 00:24:17.969
in geto, bay undz in Byalistok.

00:24:17.969 --> 00:24:19.904
dos heyst, oybe du vest aroysgeyn,

00:24:19.904 --> 00:24:22.330
un oyb du vest araynbrengen broyt,

00:24:22.330 --> 00:24:26.245
un oybe du vest epes ganvenen, oybe du vest hobn tsu ton mit polyakn,

00:24:26.245 --> 00:24:31.089
zolstu visn az dir drot toyt, hobn zey oyfgegongen dray mentshn,

00:24:31.089 --> 00:24:34.026
glaykh. dos iz geven dos ershte vokh vos zey zaynen arayn in geto.

00:24:33.592 --> 00:24:36.153
du host gezen mit di eygene oygn?

00:24:34.719 --> 00:24:40.558
ikh bin geshtanen derbay, ikh bin geshtanen derbay, vayl me hot dir getsvungen! me hot dir getsvungen zolst shteyn un zolst zen vos zey tuen.

00:24:40.592 --> 00:24:43.451
un ikh hob davke eynem fun di yugntlekhe gekent.

00:24:44.229 --> 00:24:45.620
vi hot er geheysn?

00:24:45.399 --> 00:24:46.478
Yablonko.

00:24:46.478 --> 00:24:48.876
Yosl, zest? me dermont im yetst.

00:24:48.952 --> 00:24:49.812
ye.

00:24:51.463 --> 00:24:52.850
Yosl Yablonko?

00:24:52.820 --> 00:24:53.220
ye.

00:24:55.867 --> 00:24:58.712
er iz geven fun di oyfgehongene. un dan,

00:24:58.712 --> 00:25:02.152
ot azoy iz ongegangen etlekhe khadoshim,

00:25:03.037 --> 00:25:06.174
biz februar nayntsn,

00:25:07.910 --> 00:25:10.046
di aktsye iz geven in nayntsn...

00:25:09.356 --> 00:25:12.301
dray un fir, dra- dray un fertsik.

00:25:10.378 --> 00:25:12.854
dray un fer- in fertsik iz dos geven?

00:25:12.973 --> 00:25:15.024
in februar fir un fertsik.

00:25:15.186 --> 00:25:18.833
hot ir gedarft trogn a mogn-doved?

00:25:18.612 --> 00:25:20.918
neyn, mir hobn getrogn gele lates.

00:25:20.918 --> 00:25:24.429
eyne fun der rekhter zayt un fun hintn fun der linker zayt.

00:25:24.569 --> 00:25:26.216
dos iz geven a mogn-doved?

00:25:25.973 --> 00:25:31.365
dos iz geven, ye, a gele late iz geven a groyser mogn-doved, ober nisht keyn kleyner, a groyser, m'hot dos gezen.

00:25:31.760 --> 00:25:33.137
m'hot es gemuzt zen.

00:25:33.137 --> 00:25:36.024
mir zo- mir hobn nisht getort aroysgeyn fun shtub on der late.

00:25:36.483 --> 00:25:39.137
in andere pletser hot men getrogn

00:25:39.137 --> 00:25:44.307
ARM-bender azelkhe, mit mogn-doveds, ober bay undz iz geven di gele late,

00:25:44.307 --> 00:25:45.513
di gantse tsayt.

00:25:45.590 --> 00:25:48.137
tsi hot a mol a yid prubirt

00:25:48.137 --> 00:25:51.939
aroptsunemen di late un aroystsukrikhn, aroystsuganvenen?

00:25:51.803 --> 00:25:53.216
zeyer a sakh.

00:25:53.216 --> 00:25:55.290
zeyer a sakh yunge mentshn

00:25:56.000 --> 00:25:57.460
hobn zikh bamit

00:25:58.890 --> 00:26:01.040
aroystsugeyn, aroystsuganvenen.

00:26:01.040 --> 00:26:04.136
in onheyb fun der, ven mir zaynen arayn in geto,

00:26:04.136 --> 00:26:08.534
un mayn mame zayendik akht un draysik yor, hot zikh nokh gefilt zeyer yung.

00:26:08.534 --> 00:26:10.895
un zi hot gedenkt di alte daytshn,

00:26:10.895 --> 00:26:12.704
flegt zi aropnemen di lates,

00:26:12.704 --> 00:26:15.859
un adurkhkrikhn, adurkhkrikhn dem parkan,

00:26:15.859 --> 00:26:19.236
un avekgeyn in dorf kedey tsu brengen broyt far undz.

00:26:19.236 --> 00:26:21.072
dos iz geven in onfang.

00:26:21.072 --> 00:26:25.625
ober shpeter hot men yedn tog geshosn etlekhe mentshn vos hobn es geton.

00:26:25.625 --> 00:26:29.731
hob ikh dan gevornt mayn mame az zi zol zayn in shtub un ikh vel es ton.

00:26:29.731 --> 00:26:33.816
bin ikh, zog ikh, "ikh vel geyn tsu der arbet vel ikh legal, ve- ot vet men mir nit dershisn,

00:26:33.816 --> 00:26:35.518
ober dir vet men dershisn."

00:26:35.518 --> 00:26:36.859
iz zi geblibn in shtub.

00:26:36.859 --> 00:26:38.831
ober vegn yunge mentshn

00:26:39.375 --> 00:26:45.703
zaynen a groyse grupe yunge mentshn aropgerisn di late un avek in partizaner. zey hobn gevust az ⟨es⟩ zaynen faran velder,

00:26:46.886 --> 00:26:50.171
un ikh muz zikh dermonen vi di velder hobn gegeysn vos zaynen geven

00:26:50.171 --> 00:26:54.830
groys groyse grupn partizaner. zaynen yunge mentshn aroys.

00:26:54.830 --> 00:27:00.660
zaynen aroys mentshn vos hobn zikh bahaltn oyf der arisher zayt. vos zeyer poylish iz geven zeyer gut.

00:27:00.660 --> 00:27:02.469
farshteyst? un der oyszen.

00:27:02.588 --> 00:27:04.730
kedey zolst geyn oyfn gas,

00:27:04.730 --> 00:27:06.964
di polyakn hobn zeyer gut ⟨der⟩kent di yidn,

00:27:06.964 --> 00:27:09.645
zeyer gut. iz di moyre geven azoy groys.

00:27:09.645 --> 00:27:12.702
di daytshn hobn nisht azoy gekent derkenen keyn yidn

00:27:12.758 --> 00:27:14.900
vi di polyakn hobn es geton.

00:27:14.900 --> 00:27:15.900
farshteyst?

00:27:15.900 --> 00:27:18.432
iz, di vos hobn ⟨oysgeven⟩ blond

00:27:18.432 --> 00:27:20.681
un zey hobn gegat a mer arishn oyszen,

00:27:20.681 --> 00:27:24.730
zaynen aroys un probirt far gelt koyfn a plats

00:27:24.730 --> 00:27:28.276
un bazorgn zayn oyf der, oyf der arisher zayt.

00:27:28.374 --> 00:27:29.964
glaykhtsaytik hobn

00:27:32.084 --> 00:27:33.174
yidn

00:27:34.324 --> 00:27:36.704
zikh bahaltn, di vos hobn nisht gegat

00:27:36.704 --> 00:27:39.318
keyn arishn oyszen.

00:27:39.438 --> 00:27:45.110
gehat noente polyakn, mentshn hobn gehat dinstn bay velkhe zey hobn gegarbe-, vos zey hobn gearbet bay yidn,

00:27:45.110 --> 00:27:47.027
mentshn zaynen gevorn raykhe yidn,

00:27:47.027 --> 00:27:50.914
vos zey hobn gegat fabrikn vos yidn, vos polyakn hobn bay zey gearbet.

00:27:51.033 --> 00:27:54.509
hot men far zey griber oysgegrobn.

00:27:54.905 --> 00:27:59.381
unter der heym hot men genumen, lekher gemakht un zey bahaltn dortn.

00:27:59.437 --> 00:28:02.473
un a teyl hot zikh oysgebahaltn

00:28:02.473 --> 00:28:05.169
un ibergelebt di milkhome oyf aza min oyfn.
